                        <p>Of the quires <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܕ</foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܗ</foreign> are missing, <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܒ</foreign>,<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܓ</foreign>, and <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܚ</foreign> are imperfect; so that there are lacunae after foll. <locus from="9">9</locus> and <locus from="19">19</locus>.</p>
